Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:35.00,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.80,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't paying attention either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:38.54,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Your bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:39.65,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:41.52,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Were there any eggs inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.66,CRGintama2,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.08,CRGintama2,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anything important inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.08,CRGintama2,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Really, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:46.85,CRGintama2,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:48.18,CRGintama2,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:50.83,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:52.29,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.06,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:57.02,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like anpan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:03.89,OnScreen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Meals Should Be Balanced
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.64,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.26,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Anpan and milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.98,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I run a stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.12,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't eat anything else until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:19.57,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's an offering to the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.91,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I personally can't stand it, but the god of stakeouts is a big fan, so that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.21,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,A truth that has been shown in police dramas around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:28.43,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,For the success of this stakeout,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:32.25,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I must suppress my desire to eat curry, katsudon, and yakiniku,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.70,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,and munch on anpan instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:38.37,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to come into contact with the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.81,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,And you're supposed to be an inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:44.04,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how weird it is to stake out a stakeout?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:47.89,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,You should have volunteered if you have nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.27,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.88,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you're only eating anpan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.02,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You can be superstitious if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.63,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,but you won't last long if you aren't eating right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.28,CR Gintama,Ramen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.02,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:02.66,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even bother, Vice Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.82,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:08.25,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist, I suppose I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.28,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,An order from you is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.51,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.89,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:19.22,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,So how would you describe this Sachi Narasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.34,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be a nice person,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.44,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,going by the five days I've been watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:27.72,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I find it hard to believe that she's the older sister of a brutal Joi terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.67,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.00,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at Sogo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:34.98,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,one sibling tends to be more responsible when the other is anything but.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.81,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Chief, you're a little too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.92,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And what about Donbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.01,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,He's been running around like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.33,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he stole money from his fellow terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:48.34,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to chase him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.85,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,His only option is to run to his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:55.77,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I like the idea of using his sister as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:04:00.01,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like the idea of letting her brother run wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:06.63,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what if the Joi who are chasing Donbei decide to use her as bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:13.02,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use his sister as bait to wipe them all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.05,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the dirty work to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.98,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yamazaki, I'm giving you a different mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.99,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.61,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sagaru Yamazaki's Observation Report:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:26.20,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Week 1 of Living on Anpan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.87,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living on anpan for an entire week now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.66,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What I'd give for a bowl of miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.77,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The girl hasn't made a move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.97,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sachi Narasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.74,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Owner of the bar Nonbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.23,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The story is that she's a dutiful daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:41.93,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,who's been running her father's business by herself since he died four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:47.46,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, her brother Donbei is notorious for being a nasty villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:52.01,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,He regularly came to his sister for money after she took over the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.43,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,A dutiful daughter under duress,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.28,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,the younger brother who continues to put her in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.38,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,and the terrorists who are after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:04.24,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is to monitor the Joi terrorists,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.99,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,while protecting the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.99,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I, Sagaru Yamazaki, Shinsengumi inspector, vow to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.67,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And with my newfound determination, I once again munch on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.15,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 8 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.54,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to the supermarket yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.65,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear people whispering, "Anpanman is here! No kidding!" in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:24.88,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Nonbei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.93,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,but the girl hasn't made a move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:27.39,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Her customers are all regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.80,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Every day is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.69,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can only hope that her peaceful life lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:36.03,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,As I begin to forget my purpose here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:38.34,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I once again munch on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.02,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 12 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.47,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized that it's been days since I've talked to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:48.91,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The last words I spoke were, "No, put it in one bag," three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.72,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,but the girl hasn't made a move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:55.16,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,For a moment, I almost thought that she was looking at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:56.54,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Nonbei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.87,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,but it must have been my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.86,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,As I try to pull myself together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.75,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I once again munch on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.85,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I could only finish half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:05.06,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 15 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.57,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to the convenience store,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.09,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,people started whispering, "The one-bag guy is here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.26,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,"He's gonna buy anpan and milk!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.78,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,"In one bag!" and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:17.43,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Nonbei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.34,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,but the girl hasn't made a move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:18.24,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do if nothing happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.77,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,As I attempt to ignore those doubts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.71,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I once again munch on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.69,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And then I throw it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.99,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 20 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.16,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I last spoke that I was wondering if my voice still worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.61,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,so I screamed at the top of my lungs and the guy next door replied,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.62,CR Gintama,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Shut up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.83,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,while banging on the wall, which had me jumping up and down with joy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.51,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,over the fact that I actually held a conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.87,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,but the girl still hasn't made a move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:44.63,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,She just smiles day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.69,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,There are more exciting ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:52.33,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Such as harboring a fugitive younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:55.27,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And with that thought, I once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.10,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,...smash anpan against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.35,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 22 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.17,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.01,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,When is her younger brother going to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:06.88,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,When will I be released from this anpan curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:07.84,CR Gintama,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.14,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, younger brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:13.29,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Save me from the endless anpan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.16,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,As I make a wish from the bottom of my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.08,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I sparking the anpan into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.25,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 23 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.58,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I sparking the anpan into the supermarket clerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.00,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 24 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.59,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I sparking the anpan into the convenience store clerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.84,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 25 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.93,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I sparking the anpan into the vice chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.26,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 28 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:37.05,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I wake up and discover that I have no memory of the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.58,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,However, despite all the change I've gone through,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.41,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,the girl hasn't made a move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.98,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like always, she scatters anpan on the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:43.98,CR Gintama,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6]Anpan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.94,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,and puts the anpan above the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.53,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And then at anpan-night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.98,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,she anpans the anpan and anpans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:54.38,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Anpanning the anpan to anpan the anpan and anpanny anpan, anpan, anpan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.20,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Day 30 of Living on Anpan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.71,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,ANPAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.40,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 31 of living on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:13.09,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, I was standing in an unfamiliar place, covered in anko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.97,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a damn about the mission or girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.10,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to take another bite of anpan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:23.07,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.64,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer cared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.23,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I headed back to the room to pack up and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.36,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,But there I found...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.01,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize we were neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.46,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll ruin your health if you only eat anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.95,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here are some leftover meat and potatoes if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.02,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.46,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,From Nonbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:49.13,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The tears wouldn't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:52.62,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when she realized I was watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:55.09,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much she actually knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.18,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,One thing was clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.70,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't worthy of her gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:04.39,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was ready to abandon her because of my stupid superstition...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.63,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I turned against the god of stakeouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.53,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(360,1)}Greater Edo Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.42,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 3 of meat and potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.03,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:21.17,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,...to find myself staring at an unfamiliar ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.65,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And the vice chief with a disgusted look on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.71,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Chief, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.79,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,The hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:28.40,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.51,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.46,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What about Sachi-san? Her brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.92,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.43,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,They got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.39,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.76,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,They took the money and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.28,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.94,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We were tricked by the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:46.50,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The siblings were working together to steal money from the Joi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.47,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The sister noticed my presence immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:52.49,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,so she spent an entire month acting to fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.46,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And once I fell apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.57,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,she used the pretense of kindness to poison me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:01.18,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Women are damn scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:04.26,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding under layer after layer of makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.21,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Do we ever get a chance to see their real faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:10.68,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she still served as the perfect bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:14.81,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We rounded up all the ruffians who were trailing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.75,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That more than makes up for the two who got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:22.13,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to freely move around because you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.94,CR Gintama,Ramen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.88,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yamazaki, you did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:35.23,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Chief, this isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:38.16,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.44,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm depressed or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:44.61,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to being fooled by women and failing missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:48.11,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I was hoping that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.46,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,...I could at least lose on my own terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:56.16,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that you aren't in the mood for ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.47,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:02.69,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,It really worked, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:06.37,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,We have enough money to fool around for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.48,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.92,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.84,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Money isn't meant for fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:13.00,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Money is used to earn more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:13.98,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.91,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:19.10,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had a feeling that someone was watching us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:19.98,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:24.77,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,Are your senses shot after spending all that time with that Shinsengumi failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.32,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.27,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.44,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.76,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.31,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry to get to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.96,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Anpan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:33.95,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.29,CR Gintama,Donbei,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this festival, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:41.13,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right here. The Yamazaki Spring Bread Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.39,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Day 63 of the Yamazaki Bread Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:57.08,CR Gintama,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You really like anpan, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.77,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.77,CR Gintama,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I once again munch on anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.19,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:09.08,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to be a fan of baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.86,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.14,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.92,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.72,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I said that I'd be happy to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.91,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.43,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Happy to accompany me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.40,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.93,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What'd you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.30,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I'd be happy to watch the baseball game with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.47,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Ho... Ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.27,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.94,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you destroyed the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:38.82,OnScreen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,We Are All Warriors in the Battle Against Fate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:43.07,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,A true man isn't measured by high education, high income, or height.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.93,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The three Hs mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.31,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The only H you need is the H for the hair on your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:54.38,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,One ass hair and constant persistence is all it takes to penetrate that giant wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:58.78,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you girly men probably wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.13,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,He's not really girly, he just eats shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.68,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your trap, you sick bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.86,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.92,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,As a fellow sadist, I can guess what's in her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:08.95,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.77,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let jealousy cloud your judgment, Benny, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:11.64,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,BENNIE K?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.73,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,I don't listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:16.91,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The rain dripping from the roof can carve a hole in stone after enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:22.61,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,My relentless rain of love has finally spread open her tightly shut legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.40,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Your metaphors are too obscene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.05,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:28.98,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.11,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be waiting in front of the station at one on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:35.02,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,And she told me to stop following her around after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.27,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,And to never visit her business again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.69,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll be in a relationship now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.66,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,So that won't be needed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:46.91,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she telling you to completely forget about her after indulging you one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.85,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  'Kay, Hayashiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.18,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Pa Hayashiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.46,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the last time, I won't get another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.29,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I will make her mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:14:01.57,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hit a walk-off home run and lead Otae-san back to the bench!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:05.84,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We're right in the path of the typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.89,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,She's not gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.91,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.47,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little early,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:15.35,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,but a gentleman is supposed to arrive early and wait for the lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.46,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.56,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.64,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The weather will improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.94,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's raining cats or dogs or spears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:27.20,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,my rain of love will never falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.17,CR Gintama,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,There's something lodged in your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.72,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.70,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.75,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,A cargo plane is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:36.03,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Part of its load is falling towards Edo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:36.99,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:37.92,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.03,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna drop right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:41.49,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,It really is raining spears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.44,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,How bad is my luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.55,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm like a sponge for bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.70,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.08,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.43,CR Gintama,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe to run out into the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.29,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.49,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:00.42,CR Gintama,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.24,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even made it fifty meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.92,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,and I've already experienced fifty years worth of bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.81,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I'm going on this date!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.52,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,First, I need the tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:11.60,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.24,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these tickets for the game today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.21,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.58,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough to play baseball because of the typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.52,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go watch the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.10,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.60,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Could you let me see those tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.97,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, old timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:23.75,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.34,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you're covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:28.28,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I just dropped my tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.78,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably the ones you're holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.71,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Could you return them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.18,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.68,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,You got any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.72,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.84,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give you something better in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.82,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.33,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, we have nothing to do because of the typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.50,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Play baseball with us in the gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.95,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.23,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.00,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,And it's just a bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:58.19,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura's pitches are always so thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.01,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Old timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:01.54,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,The catcher is supposed to catch the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.05,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.48,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I need to get going soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.52,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.22,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want these tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.12,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.24,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Let me throw the ball next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:14.20,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but battery mates with the China girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.09,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.75,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.03,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, old timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.55,CR Gintama,Yo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.54,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Beetle King - Throwaway Matches\NKind of serious contest!\NThere will be kind of serious battles now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.95,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let us know which match was obviously thrown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.67,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.09,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bruised all over, and it was just a waste of time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.69,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Some evil force is actively interfering with my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.05,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you found something nice there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:41.23,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You should go with your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.94,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he like baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.06,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if he'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.53,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't left his room ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.31,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.73,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you find those tickets, China girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.71,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.53,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko-chan did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.27,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:53.80,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Those belong to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.17,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in a lot of trouble without them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.24,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.21,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were a gift from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.41,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.15,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't drop them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.68,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:08.38,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:11.45,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,This could be a chance to get your brother to go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.36,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:17.92,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Anything baseball would be like salt on an old wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:21.40,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,My brother used to love baseball so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.78,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He would always play catch with our father by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.68,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I loved to watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:32.90,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, my brother threw the ball too high,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.36,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,and our father went after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.85,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.91,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,...come home since.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:46.06,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,How far did our father go chasing after it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:52.82,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's been waiting for him to come back with the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.59,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.50,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.07,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:03.60,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.31,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.51,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.40,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.18,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop throwing balls into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:14.67,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Baseballs are meant to be thrown forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:18.53,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel your ball touch my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.06,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your old man felt the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:24.08,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping my brother come outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.75,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job, gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.04,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use my full strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:27.74,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.36,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to feel my true strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.59,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.40,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:35.09,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:38.28,CR Gintama,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.72,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone interfering with my love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:46.40,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the heavens are trying to keep me away from Otae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.23,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,But I refuse to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.19,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I can still hit a walk-off home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.51,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,You found our father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:53.01,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.32,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,He's lost his memory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.08,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.13,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Something to help him remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.31,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.70,CR Gintama,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What is this burning passion in my chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.94,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.71,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Your memory's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:09.63,CR Gintama,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:12.47,CR Gintama,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered everything by playing catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.16,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:17.32,CR Gintama,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.83,CR Gintama,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way to thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.05,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.64,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you've finally been reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:27.46,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you should go enjoy the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.04,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.17,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.44,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.61,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.20,CR Gintama,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,We'll return the favor one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.58,CR Gintama,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:40.67,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm already late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:45.33,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that Otae-san and I aren't meant to be together in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:51.47,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Fate has chosen to stand in our way, and there's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:55.69,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,As I watched the skies clear the moment I relinquished the tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.63,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,that was the conclusion I reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.96,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Otae-san is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.88,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.49,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.26,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Toshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.50,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's not your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.69,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, the girl doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.47,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm devoting myself to the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.77,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.42,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you while you're down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.10,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,but we have a problem on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.05,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,A meteorite is approaching Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:21.94,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.22,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.06,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,The meteorite's the size of a baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:28.67,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's so small that they couldn't detect it until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.52,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,but at this rate, it's going to hit your date spot in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.96,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.91,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to issue an evacuation order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.54,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there probably won't be much damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.08,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,but you better stay away from the dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.29,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.53,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:44.76,CR Gintama,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.22,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.22,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,The meteorite is headed right for Otae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:54.19,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was trying to defy fate and make Otae-san mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:58.11,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,fate is going after Otae-san now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.24,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.64,CR Gintama,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.42,CR Gintama,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.85,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.37,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Is it coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.83,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,...for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:10.54,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:14.88,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo will pinch hit for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.33,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.74,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:19.62,CR Gintama,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,We've got you covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:22.61,CR Gintama,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch it if you miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.19,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:29.26,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in going to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:32.22,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I live for love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.41,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,To protect my loved ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:40.06,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I live as a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:45.61,CR Gintama,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a walk-off home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.69,CR Gintama,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm walking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:35.31,OnScreen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode\NMeals Should Be Balanced
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:31.26,CRGintama2,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:33.54,CRGintama2,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's too confusing when talking about the poster girl for a poster store,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.98,CRGintama2,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so call her a sandwich board
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:36.98,CR Gintama,,0000,0000,0000,,
